Meson is the build system used for this project. For more information
please see [mesonbuild.com](https://mesonbuild.com)

You will need the following build tools installed:

- pkg-config
- meson
- ninja

To build using meson
====================
meson setup build
cd build
ninja
sudo ninja install


Or without chdir
================
meson setup build
ninja -C build
sudo ninja -C build install


Uninstall
=========
sudo ninja -C build uninstall


Clean build
===========
rm -rf build/
